{"id": 2801, "genre": 1001, "title": "一句话证明你是一个熟知客服套路的当代人", "description": "客服话术 100 句，正在加载中……（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Images）", "record_count": 1811, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190219095839MiuHWOeb9cw0UXmk.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-08T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 338688, "content": "我们这边48小时之内给您回电。\n（4一千年了……我的回电呢？）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552609}, {"id": 338182, "content": "还有5分钟，菜正做着呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632494}, {"id": 338188, "content": "你好，优秀的人总是能平静的沟通", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632518}, {"id": 339214, "content": "您好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983148}, {"id": 339983, "content": "您好我是某某公司的，我就是给您推荐一下我们的什么什么课程，您不一定要来上的。然后说到你想骂人了还不停嘴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1598126}, {"id": 339472, "content": "＋1", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1504544}, {"id": 339984, "content": "甭管能不能解决问题，一顿客套废话耽误时间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1598126}, {"id": 338962, "content": "xxx正在为您服务。请问亲有什么需要的吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635979}, {"id": 337939, "content": "接到电话对方先沉默3秒，然后才开始噼里啪啦，好像这样我就不会挂掉一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871922}, {"id": 337940, "content": "正在为您查询，请稍后", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588015}, {"id": 337941, "content": "稍后请您为我的服务打分", "image": null, "praise_count": 164, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213698}, {"id": 337942, "content": "先生女士您好：………………", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1489446}, {"id": 338198, "content": "麻烦换人工客服来跟我说，然后。。机器人卡壳不知道说啥就自圆其说的挂了电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1586408}, {"id": 337943, "content": "无法从书面答复分辨，客服是男是女…", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 399953}, {"id": 338711, "content": "您好，我们这边……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918261}, {"id": 337944, "content": "关你啥事？\n关我啥事？\n还有这事？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623017}, {"id": 337945, "content": "您这个不归我们管的，是❌❌❌出了问题。\n❌❌❌：是⭕⭕⭕的问题。\n⭕⭕⭕：是。。的问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 108, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1471611}, {"id": 337946, "content": "好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 348026}, {"id": 338202, "content": "请对我们的服务给出评价，非常满意按1，满意按2，不满意按3\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632590}, {"id": 337947, "content": "亲，这款有货的，您付款后今天就能安排发出啦！", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631374}, {"id": 337948, "content": "n个工作日后给您答复，请保持手机畅通", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540826}, {"id": 338204, "content": "您好，欢迎致电❌❌❌❌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632596}, {"id": 337949, "content": "感谢您的致电，祝您生活愉快，再见", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631424}, {"id": 337950, "content": "这边尽量呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 198, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506154}, {"id": 337951, "content": "接电话后：喂，你好，能听到吗？（此处停顿2秒）。嗯嗯，是这样的，我们......电话录音，听第一句时就可以挂电话了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159285}, {"id": 337952, "content": "亲亲，这边不是我们能控制的呢🙂", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631438}, {"id": 337953, "content": "【亲亲，这边建议你xxxx呢😘】", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333758}, {"id": 337954, "content": "需要我帮您转到售后吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 446030}, {"id": 337955, "content": "亲亲，这边联系您再稍等一会呢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551636}, {"id": 337956, "content": "亲 我们这边没办法保证呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631460}, {"id": 337957, "content": "“请问你是怎么使用的呢”🤮需要你个刚上任的客服来教吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130789}, {"id": 337959, "content": "我们这边帮你问下快递", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1568073}, {"id": 338215, "content": "回家等电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355256}, {"id": 337960, "content": "双引号顾客反双引号：那我再看看吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396508}, {"id": 337961, "content": "祝您生活愉快 再见(ー_ー)!!", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631489}, {"id": 337962, "content": "这里是工号xxx，请问有什么可以帮您的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950098}, {"id": 338730, "content": "还有什么要说的么？\n怎么解决？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635196}, {"id": 337963, "content": "请稍候再拨", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434663}, {"id": 337965, "content": "我们会尽快处理的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619106}, {"id": 338735, "content": "请按＃号键返回，谢谢，请挂机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635239}, {"id": 337968, "content": "嗯嗯 亲亲非常抱歉哈这边催一下哦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631508}, {"id": 338736, "content": "感谢您的来电", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635333}, {"id": 337969, "content": "这个我们也是没办法的呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519185}, {"id": 337970, "content": "您好，这边可以打扰您几分钟吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, 